lines.transliteration: ša₂ ki-ma UD-mi me-he-e na-mu-u₂ ug-gat-su
u₃ ki-i ma-nit še-re-e-ti za-aq-šu₂ ṭa-a-bu
ša₂ nak-bat qa-ti-šu₂ la i-na-aš₂-šu-u₂ ša₂-ma-ʾu-u₂
{d}AMAR.UTU ša₂ nak-bat qa-ti-šu₂ la i-na-aš₂-šu-u₂ ša₂-ma-ʾu-u₂
ip-pal-la-as-ma a-na ša₂ is-ki-pu-šu₂ DINGIR-šu₂ i-sah-hur-šu₂
u₃ ki-i a-ra-ah bu-u₂-ri it-ta-na-as-ha-ra EGIR-šu₂
ina UD i-šar-ti-šu₂ up-ta-aṭ-ṭa-ru eʾ-il-tum u an-nu
ina te-e-šu₂ uš-dap-pa-ru šu-ru-up-pu-u₂ u hur-ba-šu₂
ma-na-ma ina DINGIR.MEŠ a-lak-ta-šu₂ ul i-de
a-na ki-i kab-ta-at ŠU-su ŠA₃-ba-šu₂ re-me-ni
a-na ki-i gaṣ-ṣu GIŠ.TUKUL.MEŠ-šu₂ ka-bat-ta-šu₂ muš-neš-šat
ša la ŠA₃-bi-šu₂ man-nu mi₃-hi-iṣ-ta-šu₂ li-šap-ši-ih
lu-ša₂-pi ug-gat-su ša₂ ki-ma nu-u₂-ni a-ku-lu ru-šum-tu₂
it-ti LU₂.HAL u ša₂-ʾi-i-li a-lak-ti ul par-sat
at-til-ma ina šat mu-ši šu-ut-ti par₂-da-at
a-na lem-ni u gal-le-e i-tu-ra ib-ri
ki-na-at-ti a-na na-aq da-me u₂-mar-ra-aš₂ GIŠ.TUKUL
GEME₂ ina pa-an um-ma-ni ṭa-pil-ti iq-bi
a-na ša₂ iq-bu-u₂ a-hu-lap ha-muṭ-su mu-u₂-tu
ša₂ la ka-šim-ma i-te-me ba-la-ṭu še-du-uš
ul ar-ši a-lik i-di ga-me-lu ul a-mur
a-na ṣi-in-di u bir-ti u₂-za-ʾi-zu mim-ma-a-a
